title: Smith College Orchestra Spring 2025 Concert
description: Jessica playing principal clarinet in the Smith College Orchestra Spring Concert 2025. The program includes Copland's Four Dance Episodes from Rodeo and Copland's Lincoln Portrait, narrated by Smith College President Sarah Willie-LeBreton. Conducted by Jonathan Hirsh.
